# Python ML (SignDetectionModel) — too large for GitHub; keep locally or use cloud/LFS
# Training videos (~5 GB)
GestureTalk-Backend/SignDetectionModel/wordset/videos/

# Letter/word training images and derived datasets
GestureTalk-Backend/SignDetectionModel/data/
GestureTalk-Backend/SignDetectionModel/data_word/

# Model weights and serialized training artifacts
GestureTalk-Backend/SignDetectionModel/**/*.pth
GestureTalk-Backend/SignDetectionModel/**/*.pkl
GestureTalk-Backend/SignDetectionModel/**/*.pt
GestureTalk-Backend/SignDetectionModel/**/*.onnx
GestureTalk-Backend/SignDetectionModel/**/*.pickle
GestureTalk-Backend/SignDetectionModel/mlp_model.p
GestureTalk-Backend/SignDetectionModel/data.pickle
GestureTalk-Backend/SignDetectionModel/data_word.pickle

